parameters.toolDescription:
MemoryClaw memory tools for prospect context. Parameters for each tool:
  - memory_search: {"query": "string", "userId": "<prospectId from message>"}
  - memory_add:    {"message": "string", "userId": "<prospectId from message>"}
  - memory_get:    {"path": "string", "userId": "<prospectId from message>"}
  - memory_delete: {"path": "string", "userId": "<prospectId from message>"}
Always use the prospectId from the message as userId.
